data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Baths 2 half baths house on a full basement. The house is located on a lake lot with access for property owners. The lot features an RV pad with 50 amp power, water, and septic. The lot gently rolls back to the stocked lake with a fenced-in backyard. The roof is 6 months old, the HVAC is less than two years old, and there are new hardwood floors. 2-car garages, huge attic space great for storage, partially finished basement with workshop. beautiful screened-in back porch overlooking the lake. The lake is a community lake with owner access and stocked with fish.
